---

## Terminal goal — WEAVE row in 16-cell matrix

WEAVE 는 4 disease class 각각에 cure-grade 단백질 design 제공. Meta `.roadmap.hexa_bio` §0 의 **W 행**.

| Cell  | Disease       | 후보 분자 (예)                                           |
|-------|---------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|
| W·α   | AML           | FLT3-ITD / CD33 표적 BiTE 또는 oncolytic 단백질          |
| W·β   | SCD           | mutation-corrected β-globin                               |
| W·γ   | pan-cov       | spike RBD broadly-neutralizing 항체                       |
| W·δ   | senolytic     | p16+ cell 표적 senolytic 단백질                           |

**Cell DoD**: in-silico verified design + Landauer floor margin + Π^p_2 compatibility + Π¹_1-CA₀ closure cert + witness → `state/discovery_absorption/registry.jsonl`.

